sentences: Petulla was signed to Datsik's label Firepower Records in 2012, while also releasing through other labels such as Rottun Recordings and OWSLA.
In 2017, Petulla launched his own record label, clothes shop, and artist collective known as Shred Collective.
He has been in the bass scene since 2010.
